{"tid":2306687,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中資【攜程旅行網】旗下【永安旅遊】裁員約120人，約佔編制兩成！","createTime":"2020-11-30T15:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T15:13:55.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4932f15a0e76742437cbdb37af466981d32735","tid":2306687,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T15:13:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562828-20201130.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562828-20201130.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xCBot4r0pQQ4M2eut5PfJzM%3D&h=03af13bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562828-20201130.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b31d6a6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562828-20201130.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n永安旅遊宣布削減約120名員工，人數約佔整體員工編制兩成。<br />\n<br />\n永安表示，在現時疫情下，本港及外地的出入境防疫政策仍未見放寬，令旅遊業務恢復無期，根據國際航運機構的預測，未來一至兩年亦難以回復過往的出行規模。<br />\n<br />\n現時的人員數目遠超於未來的業務需求，隨著保就業計劃結束，人力成本將帶來難以負荷的壓力，因此在迫不得已的情況下，進行適當的架構精簡和業務重組。<br />\n<br />\n受措施影響的涉及約120名員工，分佈於不同部門，公司將以一個月代通知金，按僱傭條例計算相關離職補償。至於仍然留任的員工，則需繼續放取若干天數的無薪假。"},{"pid":"24de10b5b05ce9b05c80029d681eb9a5bd50beeb","tid":2306687,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T15:13:55.000Z","msg":"明明無曬反對派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}